<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="stupid-adj">stupid <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'stjuːpɪd/    美 /'stuːpɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-foolish-silly">1.★ <strong>愚蠢的(foolish / silly)；笨的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It is stupid of you</strong> to believe that.
你真蠢，居然相信那种事。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>stupidly /'stjuːpɪdli/ adv   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Well, you’ve acted <strong><em>_</em></strong>__ (愚蠢地) and you will pay for it.  （2006 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. stupidly  </p></div>